news_header: Ukraine rejects agreements made without its involvement in negotiations.
news_original_title: Analyysi: Ukraina näkee paljon tapahtuvan sen ympärillä, muttei usko sen tuovan rauhaa
news_text: Ukraine is excluded from US-Russia talks, leading to concerns about its future and peace negotiations. President Zelensky emphasizes that any agreements without Ukraine's participation are unacceptable.
